29#ifndef __NOUVEAU_ENCODER_H__
30#define __NOUVEAU_ENCODER_H__
31
32#include <subdev/bios/dcb.h>
33
34#include <drm/drm_encoder_slave.h>
35#include "dispnv04/disp.h"
36
37#define NV_DPMS_CLEARED 0x80
38
39struct nvkm_i2c_port;
40
41struct nouveau_encoder {
42 struct drm_encoder_slave base;
43
44 struct dcb_output *dcb;
45 int or;
46
47 struct i2c_adapter *i2c;
48 struct nvkm_i2c_aux *aux;
49
50 /* different to drm_encoder.crtc, this reflects what's
51 * actually programmed on the hw, not the proposed crtc */
52 struct drm_crtc *crtc;
53 u32 ctrl;
54
55 struct drm_display_mode mode;
56 int last_dpms;
57
58 struct nv04_output_reg restore;
59
60 union {
61 struct {
62 u8 dpcd[8];
63 int link_nr;
64 int link_bw;
65 u32 datarate;
66 } dp;
67 };
68};
69
70struct nouveau_encoder *
71find_encoder(struct drm_connector *connector, int type);
72
73static inline struct nouveau_encoder *nouveau_encoder(struct drm_encoder *enc)
74{
75 struct drm_encoder_slave *slave = to_encoder_slave(enc);
76
77 return container_of(slave, struct nouveau_encoder, base);
78}
79
80static inline struct drm_encoder *to_drm_encoder(struct nouveau_encoder *enc)
81{
82 return &enc->base.base;
83}
84
85static inline struct drm_encoder_slave_funcs *
86get_slave_funcs(struct drm_encoder *enc)
87{
88 return to_encoder_slave(enc)->slave_funcs;
89}
90
91/* nouveau_dp.c */
92int nouveau_dp_detect(struct nouveau_encoder *);
93
94struct nouveau_connector *
95nouveau_encoder_connector_get(struct nouveau_encoder *encoder);
96
97#endif /* __NOUVEAU_ENCODER_H__ */
